{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1112,"text":"Hi."},{"time":2461,"text":"Let me ask the audience a question:"},{"time":4831,"text":"Did you ever lie as a child?"},{"time":7050,"text":"If you did, could you please\nraise your hand?"},{"time":11145,"text":"Wow! This is the most honest\ngroup of people I've ever met."}]},{"cues":[{"time":14623,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":16604,"text":"So for the last 20 years,"},{"time":18337,"text":"I've been studying\nhow children learn to tell lies."},{"time":21776,"text":"And today, I'm going to share with you"},{"time":24104,"text":"some of the discoveries we have made."}]},{"cues":[{"time":26624,"text":"But to begin, I'm going to tell you\na story from Mr. Richard Messina,"},{"time":31573,"text":"who is my friend and an elementary\nschool principal."},{"time":35266,"text":"He got a phone call one day."},{"time":39279,"text":"The caller says,"},{"time":40454,"text":"\"Mr. Messina, my son Johnny\nwill not come to school today"},{"time":44360,"text":"because he's sick.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":46498,"text":"Mr. Messina asks,"},{"time":48258,"text":"\"Who am I speaking to, please?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":50788,"text":"And the caller says,"},{"time":52302,"text":"\"I am my father.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":53991,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":58227,"text":"So this story --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":59933,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":61489,"text":"sums up very nicely\nthree common beliefs we have"},{"time":65823,"text":"about children and lying."},{"time":68140,"text":"One, children only come to tell lies"},{"time":72795,"text":"after entering elementary school."},{"time":75552,"text":"Two, children are poor liars."},{"time":77887,"text":"We adults can easily detect their lies."},{"time":80768,"text":"And three, if children lie\nat a very young age,"},{"time":84830,"text":"there must be some\ncharacter flaws with them,"},{"time":87703,"text":"and they are going to become\npathological liars for life."},{"time":92720,"text":"Well, it turns out"},{"time":94938,"text":"all of the three beliefs are wrong."}]},{"cues":[{"time":98617,"text":"We have been playing guessing games"},{"time":101351,"text":"with children all over the world."},{"time":103457,"text":"Here is an example."},{"time":104967,"text":"So in this game, we asked children\nto guess the numbers on the cards."},{"time":109958,"text":"And we tell them if they win the game,"},{"time":112860,"text":"they are going to get a big prize."},{"time":115525,"text":"But in the middle of the game,"},{"time":117026,"text":"we make an excuse and leave the room."},{"time":121763,"text":"And before we leave the room,"},{"time":123721,"text":"we tell them not to peek at the cards."},{"time":127518,"text":"Of course,"},{"time":128958,"text":"we have hidden cameras in the room"},{"time":131143,"text":"to watch their every move."},{"time":134216,"text":"Because the desire\nto win the game is so strong,"},{"time":137657,"text":"more than 90 percent of children will peek"},{"time":141167,"text":"as soon as we leave the room."}]},{"cues":[{"time":142628,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":145044,"text":"The crucial question is:"},{"time":147054,"text":"When we return and ask the children"},{"time":149826,"text":"whether or not they have peeked,"},{"time":152159,"text":"will the children who peeked confess"},{"time":155235,"text":"or lie about their transgression?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":159525,"text":"We found that regardless\nof gender, country, religion,"},{"time":164934,"text":"at two years of age,"},{"time":167188,"text":"30 percent lie,"},{"time":169139,"text":"70 percent tell the truth\nabout their transgression."},{"time":172972,"text":"At three years of age,"},{"time":175134,"text":"50 percent lie and 50 percent\ntell the truth."},{"time":179302,"text":"At four years of age,"},{"time":181225,"text":"more than 80 percent lie."},{"time":184334,"text":"And after four years of age,"},{"time":186809,"text":"most children lie."},{"time":189180,"text":"So as you can see,"},{"time":190567,"text":"lying is really a typical part\nof development."},{"time":194054,"text":"And some children begin to tell lies"},{"time":196868,"text":"as young as two years of age."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200438,"text":"So now, let's take a closer look\nat the younger children."},{"time":205336,"text":"Why do some but not all\nyoung children lie?"},{"time":210184,"text":"In cooking, you need good ingredients"},{"time":213537,"text":"to cook good food."},{"time":215793,"text":"And good lying requires\ntwo key ingredients."},{"time":221109,"text":"The first key ingredient\nis theory of mind,"},{"time":225243,"text":"or the mind-reading ability."},{"time":227768,"text":"Mind reading is the ability to know"},{"time":229870,"text":"that different people have\ndifferent knowledge about the situation"},{"time":234502,"text":"and the ability to differentiate\nbetween what I know"},{"time":238327,"text":"and what you know."},{"time":239914,"text":"Mind reading is important for lying"},{"time":242185,"text":"because the basis of lying is that I know"},{"time":246056,"text":"you don't know"},{"time":247231,"text":"what I know."},{"time":248406,"text":"Therefore, I can lie to you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":251070,"text":"The second key ingredient\nfor good lying is self-control."},{"time":255704,"text":"It is the ability to control your speech,\nyour facial expression"},{"time":260351,"text":"and your body language,"},{"time":261915,"text":"so that you can tell a convincing lie."},{"time":264938,"text":"And we found that those young children"},{"time":268688,"text":"who have more advanced mind-reading\nand self-control abilities"},{"time":273568,"text":"tell lies earlier"},{"time":275630,"text":"and are more sophisticated liars."},{"time":279887,"text":"As it turns out, these two abilities\nare also essential for all of us"},{"time":285530,"text":"to function well in our society."},{"time":288848,"text":"In fact, deficits in mind-reading\nand self-control abilities"},{"time":293207,"text":"are associated with serious\ndevelopmental problems,"},{"time":296790,"text":"such as ADHD and autism."},{"time":301893,"text":"So if you discover your two-year-old\nis telling his or her first lie,"},{"time":307094,"text":"instead of being alarmed,"},{"time":309102,"text":"you should celebrate --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":310618,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":312164,"text":"because it signals that your child\nhas arrived at a new milestone"},{"time":317918,"text":"of typical development."}]},{"cues":[{"time":321085,"text":"Now, are children poor liars?"},{"time":324878,"text":"Do you think you can easily\ndetect their lies?"},{"time":328745,"text":"Would you like to give it a try?"},{"time":330921,"text":"Yes? OK."},{"time":332425,"text":"So I'm going to show you two videos."},{"time":335024,"text":"In the videos,"},{"time":336199,"text":"the children are going to respond\nto a researcher's question,"},{"time":339280,"text":"\"Did you peek?\""},{"time":340786,"text":"So try to tell me"},{"time":342364,"text":"which child is lying"},{"time":343786,"text":"and which child is telling the truth."},{"time":346272,"text":"Here's child number one."},{"time":348991,"text":"Are you ready?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":351006,"text":"(Video) Adult: Did you peek? Child: No."}]},{"cues":[{"time":353619,"text":"Kang Lee: And this is child number two."}]},{"cues":[{"time":357501,"text":"(Video) Adult: Did you peek? Child: No."}]},{"cues":[{"time":361296,"text":"KL: OK, if you think\nchild number one is lying,"},{"time":364907,"text":"please raise your hand."},{"time":368401,"text":"And if you think child number two\nis lying, please raise your hand."},{"time":373593,"text":"OK, so as a matter of fact,"},{"time":376091,"text":"child number one is telling the truth,"},{"time":379052,"text":"child number two is lying."},{"time":382124,"text":"Looks like many of you are terrible\ndetectors of children's lies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":385378,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":387880,"text":"Now, we have played similar kinds of games"},{"time":391288,"text":"with many, many adults\nfrom all walks of life."},{"time":396714,"text":"And we show them many videos."},{"time":399347,"text":"In half of the videos, the children lied."},{"time":401920,"text":"In the other half of the videos,\nthe children told the truth."},{"time":406529,"text":"And let's find out\nhow these adults performed."},{"time":410319,"text":"Because there are as many liars\nas truth tellers,"},{"time":414198,"text":"if you guess randomly,"},{"time":416621,"text":"there's a 50 percent chance\nyou're going to get it right."},{"time":420715,"text":"So if your accuracy is around 50 percent,"},{"time":424333,"text":"it means you are a terrible detector\nof children's lies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":428290,"text":"So let's start with undergrads\nand law school students,"},{"time":432843,"text":"who typically have\nlimited experience with children."},{"time":438038,"text":"No, they cannot detect children's lies."},{"time":440024,"text":"Their performance is around chance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":442262,"text":"Now how about social workers\nand child-protection lawyers,"},{"time":447515,"text":"who work with children on a daily basis?"},{"time":450213,"text":"Can they detect children's lies?"},{"time":453624,"text":"No, they cannot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":454799,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":455868,"text":"What about judges,"},{"time":457364,"text":"customs officers"},{"time":459188,"text":"and police officers,"},{"time":461070,"text":"who deal with liars on a daily basis?"},{"time":463737,"text":"Can they detect children's lies?"},{"time":466800,"text":"No, they cannot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":468430,"text":"What about parents?"},{"time":469640,"text":"Can parents detect other children's lies?"},{"time":473898,"text":"No, they cannot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":475821,"text":"What about, can parents\ndetect their own children's lies?"},{"time":481208,"text":"No, they cannot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":482433,"text":"(Laughter) (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":485933,"text":"So now you may ask"},{"time":488504,"text":"why children's lies\nare so difficult to detect."},{"time":492958,"text":"Let me illustrate this\nwith my own son, Nathan."},{"time":495994,"text":"This is his facial expression"},{"time":498187,"text":"when he lies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":499595,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":501825,"text":"So when children lie,"},{"time":503451,"text":"their facial expression\nis typically neutral."},{"time":507123,"text":"However, behind this neutral expression,"},{"time":510607,"text":"the child is actually experiencing\na lot of emotions,"},{"time":513957,"text":"such as fear, guilt, shame"},{"time":517836,"text":"and maybe a little bit of liar's delight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":520956,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":523682,"text":"Unfortunately, such emotions\nare either fleeting or hidden."},{"time":528546,"text":"Therefore, it's mostly invisible to us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":531669,"text":"So in the last five years,"},{"time":533052,"text":"we have been trying to figure out a way\nto reveal these hidden emotions."},{"time":536972,"text":"Then we made a discovery."}]},{"cues":[{"time":539273,"text":"We know that underneath our facial skin,"},{"time":542482,"text":"there's a rich network of blood vessels."},{"time":545900,"text":"When we experience different emotions,"},{"time":548341,"text":"our facial blood flow changes subtly."},{"time":551613,"text":"And these changes are regulated\nby the autonomic system"},{"time":555585,"text":"that is beyond our conscious control."},{"time":558159,"text":"By looking at facial blood flow changes,"},{"time":562006,"text":"we can reveal people's hidden emotions."},{"time":565229,"text":"Unfortunately, such emotion-related\nfacial blood flow changes"},{"time":570031,"text":"are too subtle to detect by our naked eye."},{"time":573632,"text":"So to help us reveal\npeople's facial emotions,"},{"time":577424,"text":"we have developed a new imaging technology"},{"time":580482,"text":"we call \"transdermal optical imaging.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":584679,"text":"To do so, we use a regular\nvideo camera to record people"},{"time":588656,"text":"when they experience\nvarious hidden emotions."},{"time":592385,"text":"And then, using our image\nprocessing technology,"},{"time":596503,"text":"we can extract transdermal images\nof facial blood flow changes."},{"time":604475,"text":"By looking at transdermal video images,"},{"time":608771,"text":"now we can easily see"},{"time":611737,"text":"facial blood flow changes associated\nwith the various hidden emotions."},{"time":617944,"text":"And using this technology,"},{"time":619756,"text":"we can now reveal the hidden emotions\nassociated with lying,"},{"time":624448,"text":"and therefore detect people's lies."},{"time":627382,"text":"We can do so noninvasively,"},{"time":629845,"text":"remotely, inexpensively,"},{"time":632408,"text":"with an accuracy at about 85 percent,"},{"time":636092,"text":"which is far better than chance level."}]},{"cues":[{"time":639100,"text":"And in addition, we discovered\na Pinocchio effect."},{"time":644336,"text":"No, not this Pinocchio effect."}]},{"cues":[{"time":646415,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":647446,"text":"This is the real Pinocchio effect."},{"time":649592,"text":"When people lie,"},{"time":651033,"text":"the facial blood flow\non the cheeks decreases,"},{"time":654836,"text":"and the facial blood flow\non the nose increases."}]},{"cues":[{"time":659379,"text":"Of course, lying is not the only situation"},{"time":662910,"text":"that will evoke our hidden emotions."},{"time":665782,"text":"So then we asked ourselves,"},{"time":667680,"text":"in addition to detecting lies,"},{"time":670051,"text":"how can our technology be used?"},{"time":673027,"text":"One application is in education."},{"time":676597,"text":"For example, using this technology,\nwe can help this mathematics teacher"},{"time":681282,"text":"to identify the student in his classroom"},{"time":684213,"text":"who may experience high anxiety\nabout the topic he's teaching"},{"time":688982,"text":"so that he can help him."},{"time":691337,"text":"And also we can use this in health care."},{"time":694101,"text":"For example, every day I Skype my parents,"},{"time":697493,"text":"who live thousands of miles away."},{"time":700178,"text":"And using this technology,"},{"time":702023,"text":"I can not only find out\nwhat's going on in their lives"},{"time":705529,"text":"but also simultaneously monitor\ntheir heart rate, their stress level,"},{"time":711855,"text":"their mood and whether or not\nthey are experiencing pain."},{"time":715839,"text":"And perhaps in the future,"},{"time":717673,"text":"their risks for heart attack\nor hypertension."},{"time":721701,"text":"And you may ask:"},{"time":723472,"text":"Can we use this also to reveal\npoliticians' emotions?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":728977,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":730541,"text":"For example, during a debate."},{"time":733220,"text":"Well, the answer is yes."},{"time":735167,"text":"Using TV footage,"},{"time":737135,"text":"we could detect\nthe politicians' heart rate,"},{"time":741205,"text":"mood and stress,"},{"time":743275,"text":"and perhaps in the future,\nwhether or not they are lying to us."},{"time":747495,"text":"We can also use this\nin marketing research,"},{"time":750515,"text":"for example, to find out"},{"time":752390,"text":"whether or not people like\ncertain consumer products."},{"time":757229,"text":"We can even use it in dating."},{"time":759904,"text":"So for example,"},{"time":761088,"text":"if your date is smiling at you,"},{"time":763706,"text":"this technology can help you to determine"},{"time":766524,"text":"whether she actually likes you"},{"time":769155,"text":"or she is just trying to be nice to you."},{"time":771864,"text":"And in this case,"},{"time":773583,"text":"she is just trying to be nice to you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":775483,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":779244,"text":"So transdermal optical imaging technology"},{"time":782977,"text":"is at a very early stage of development."},{"time":785579,"text":"Many new applications will come about\nthat we don't know today."},{"time":790293,"text":"However, one thing I know for sure"},{"time":793095,"text":"is that lying will never\nbe the same again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":796533,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":797715,"text":"Xiè xie."}]},{"cues":[{"time":799063,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}